        "subject": "LU-14195 ldiskfs: update osd-ldiskfs for Linux 5.10",
        "message": "LU-14195 ldiskfs: update osd-ldiskfs for Linux 5.10\n\nLinux 5.10 removes EXT4_GET_BLOCKS_KEEP_SIZE and\nLDISKFS_INODE_EOFBLOCKS.\n\nLDISKFS_INODE_EOFBLOCKS isn't a #define so we cannot test is directly,\nbut we can test the related LDISKFS_EOFBLOCKS_FL\n\nTest-Parameters: trivial\nSigned-off-by: Mr NeilBrown <neilb@suse.de>\nChange-Id: I164368678fb0ab7ee3be9a7269e8ed319f7a733f\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
